main event: Captain Barney Ross, a retired US Marine Corps officer, reported sighting an unconventional aircraft over Holloman AFB, New Mexico on March 9, 1950.
interesting points: The object was disc-shaped and hovered over the base for several minutes.
The object then ascended vertically and disappeared.
Captain Ross provided details about the object's movements and characteristics.
witnesses: Captain Barney Ross, US Marine Corps (Ret)
